1
00:03:03,141 --> 00:03:05,050
We've been living peacefully outside the border

2
00:03:05,158 --> 00:03:07,589
Why must we come back here?

3
00:03:07,698 --> 00:03:10,438
lt's been 10 years. Have you come back for her ?!

4
00:03:13,648 --> 00:03:16,743
No. The reason for my return is that, l hear...

5
00:03:16,849 --> 00:03:19,174
the Plum Blossom Bandit has reappeared

6
00:03:19,284 --> 00:03:22,308
Yes, what's that got to do with us?

7
00:03:22,415 --> 00:03:24,039
Twenty years ago, the Plum Blossom Bandit

8
00:03:24,155 --> 00:03:26,692
was a well known master in the martial world

9
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:30,382
He has harmed a lot of people

10
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,436
l wanted to look for him 10 years ago

11
00:03:33,549 --> 00:03:35,493
He just vanished suddenly

12
00:03:35,601 --> 00:03:39,206
l think he might want to look me up now

13
00:03:39,325 --> 00:03:41,127
lnspite of knowing all this...

14
00:03:41,238 --> 00:03:42,827
then what are you doing back?

15
00:03:44,752 --> 00:03:48,357
He must have gone to look for me at my old house

16
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:51,112
Are you worried that he might hurt your cousin?

17
00:03:52,371 --> 00:03:54,908
lf you love her so much...

18
00:03:55,016 --> 00:03:56,925
Why did you let her marry Long Xiaoyun?

19
00:03:58,286 --> 00:04:00,432
l know that he once saved your life

20
00:04:00,547 --> 00:04:03,322
But l've never heard of anyone who would...

21
00:04:03,436 --> 00:04:05,512
give up his fiancee and property for gratitude

22
00:04:06,984 --> 00:04:09,130
That happened ten years ago

23
00:04:09,837 --> 00:04:14,143
There's no need to bring it up

24
00:05:03,347 --> 00:05:06,608
Aren't you cold? You want a sip of wine?

25
00:05:10,653 --> 00:05:11,968
Are you deaf?

26
00:05:14,932 --> 00:05:18,122
So you're not deaf. Have a sip

27
00:05:18,238 --> 00:05:19,246
l can't afford it

28
00:05:19,594 --> 00:05:22,298
Don't worry, it's my treat

29
00:05:22,657 --> 00:05:25,646
l don't want to take things from others

30
00:05:25,753 --> 00:05:28,943
l don't want to drink wine which l didn't buy

31
00:05:29,823 --> 00:05:32,396
Have l made myself clear?

32
00:05:33,756 --> 00:05:34,823
Yes, quite

33
00:05:34,938 --> 00:05:35,874
Then please leave

34
00:05:35,982 --> 00:05:38,199
l will

35
00:05:38,313 --> 00:05:41,468
Say, when you can afford it...

36
00:05:41,583 --> 00:05:42,757
will you treat me to a drink?

37
00:05:42,871 --> 00:05:45,231
Certainly

38
00:06:06,668 --> 00:06:10,107
Sit down please

39
00:06:21,212 --> 00:06:22,908
Over there

40
00:06:23,612 --> 00:06:24,821
Your wine, young master

41
00:06:33,632 --> 00:06:36,787
There're a few from the Golden Lion Escort Agency

42
00:06:36,902 --> 00:06:38,562
They're escorting something from out of town

43
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:41,596
Number two

44
00:06:41,704 --> 00:06:43,400
Do you remember that time we came across

45
00:06:43,513 --> 00:06:45,173
... the Four Tigers of Tai Xing?

46
00:06:45,287 --> 00:06:47,303
How can l forget? That day they tried

47
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:49,735
... to steal from you

48
00:06:49,845 --> 00:06:52,312
But they are no match for you

49
00:07:07,484 --> 00:07:10,959
So you're 'Sudden Wind Sword' Zhuge Lei?

50
00:07:11,068 --> 00:07:13,428
May l ask your names? Sorry l didn't recognize

51
00:07:13,887 --> 00:07:17,813
You aren't worthy of knowing our names

52
00:07:17,922 --> 00:07:20,519
Just leave what you are escorting

53
00:07:20,636 --> 00:07:22,296
... and we'll spare your life

54
00:07:22,411 --> 00:07:23,964
Put down your swords

55
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,609
And we'll let you live

56
00:07:59,151 --> 00:08:03,113
Are you 'The Black and White Snake?''

57
00:08:03,534 --> 00:08:07,175
Well, at least you've heard of us !

58
00:08:08,232 --> 00:08:10,070
Since the two want this package

59
00:08:10,388 --> 00:08:11,633
Go on, take it

60
00:08:17,382 --> 00:08:19,434
Looks like there's another grand master here

61
00:08:19,539 --> 00:08:22,041
We've almost missed you

62
00:08:24,444 --> 00:08:27,634
lf you're interested in this package

63
00:08:27,749 --> 00:08:31,082
And if you can defeat us;

64
00:08:31,195 --> 00:08:33,139
Not only we'll give this to you

65
00:08:33,247 --> 00:08:34,836
We're willing to give you our heads

66
00:08:35,230 --> 00:08:37,211
Your heads are worth nothing

67
00:08:43,197 --> 00:08:46,495
Did you say that?

68
00:08:46,607 --> 00:08:47,674
Yes

69
00:08:49,147 --> 00:08:52,516
lt's a pity mine is worthless

70
00:08:52,625 --> 00:08:56,895
lt's too much, l just want 50 taels

71
00:08:57,010 --> 00:08:59,679
Fine, if you can kill me...

72
00:08:59,793 --> 00:09:00,967
l'll give you 50 taels

73
00:09:19,867 --> 00:09:21,076
My money !

74
00:09:21,608 --> 00:09:25,570
Take it, take all of it

75
00:09:53,233 --> 00:09:55,142
So, it's you !

76
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:11,594
l can afford to buy you a drink now

77
00:10:13,135 --> 00:10:14,380
With pleasure

78
00:10:26,878 --> 00:10:28,230
l look for good drinking company

79
00:10:28,338 --> 00:10:29,547
... and a good place

80
00:10:29,661 --> 00:10:31,949
l hate crowds

81
00:10:32,061 --> 00:10:33,341
Please

82
00:10:38,463 --> 00:10:40,788
Judging from the awe they had in their eyes...

83
00:10:40,898 --> 00:10:43,258
you seem like someone well known

84
00:10:46,918 --> 00:10:50,357
lt's not a good thing to be famous

85
00:10:51,335 --> 00:10:53,279
My name is Li Xunhuan, and yourself ?

86
00:10:53,389 --> 00:10:54,183
Ah Fei

87
00:10:54,294 --> 00:10:55,017
Ah Fei ?

88
00:10:55,128 --> 00:10:56,231
Right

89
00:10:56,346 --> 00:10:59,821
l'm an orphan who grew up in the wilderness

90
00:10:59,930 --> 00:11:03,228
l envy the birds flying in the sky

91
00:11:03,339 --> 00:11:04,762
Hence my name !

92
00:11:05,531 --> 00:11:08,128
Strange name indeed. Cheers

93
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:17,388
You shouldn't be drinking while coughing

94
00:11:18,752 --> 00:11:21,812
Yes, l shouldn't touch any alcohol

95
00:11:21,918 --> 00:11:23,412
Then why do you drink?

96
00:11:24,075 --> 00:11:26,648
Do you have a sad past?

97
00:11:26,754 --> 00:11:29,909
Have l asked anything you don't want to answer?

98
00:11:30,024 --> 00:11:31,198
No

99
00:11:32,564 --> 00:11:33,987
Then why did you ask?

100
00:11:34,095 --> 00:11:36,799
Okay, l won't

101
00:11:37,122 --> 00:11:40,039
Even if you want to ask, it'll have to wait

102
00:11:40,149 --> 00:11:42,295
We've got company

103
00:11:42,411 --> 00:11:47,061
Yes, one on the tree on the left

104
00:11:48,916 --> 00:11:51,169
Four at the temple ruins

105
00:11:54,101 --> 00:11:56,318
One behind the tree

106
00:12:27,744 --> 00:12:33,058
Li's Legendary Dagger, Never a miss! So overrated

107
00:12:47,158 --> 00:12:48,925
Give up the package

108
00:12:49,037 --> 00:12:50,697
And we'll leave you alone

109
00:12:50,985 --> 00:12:52,752
l've got the package

110
00:12:56,587 --> 00:13:00,513
Let's have another drink before l head off

111
00:13:08,346 --> 00:13:09,661
Go! Chase...

112
00:13:13,044 --> 00:13:14,359
Wait for me here

113
00:14:10,381 --> 00:14:12,290
Who are you?

114
00:14:13,164 --> 00:14:14,824
Li Xunhuan

115
00:14:14,938 --> 00:14:16,432
Finally you are here

116
00:14:16,539 --> 00:14:17,642
You've been waiting for me?

117
00:14:17,757 --> 00:14:19,939
A hero called Ah fey has killed many

118
00:14:20,053 --> 00:14:21,368
except one; he told me to keep an eye on him

119
00:14:21,479 --> 00:14:22,688
And wait for you

120
00:14:22,801 --> 00:14:23,310
Where's the person?

121
00:14:23,428 --> 00:14:24,436
Here

122
00:14:32,822 --> 00:14:33,581
What are you doing here?

123
00:14:33,691 --> 00:14:37,024
This is the only house around

124
00:14:37,136 --> 00:14:39,947
After l've got the package

125
00:14:40,058 --> 00:14:42,110
... l wanted to rest here for a night

126
00:14:42,216 --> 00:14:46,901
Who'd have known that your young friend's here !

127
00:14:47,677 --> 00:14:49,266
Have some tea

128
00:14:53,836 --> 00:14:54,736
Thanks

129
00:15:02,290 --> 00:15:04,306
Are you alright, sir?

130
00:15:05,074 --> 00:15:06,841
l'm not used to drinking tea

131
00:15:06,952 --> 00:15:08,446
Then have some wine

132
00:15:08,553 --> 00:15:09,276
-Do you have any? -Yes

133
00:15:09,388 --> 00:15:09,767
Great

134
00:15:09,875 --> 00:15:10,906
Just a minute

135
00:15:11,754 --> 00:15:14,079
l'll give you the package

136
00:15:14,190 --> 00:15:15,613
Please let me go

137
00:15:16,624 --> 00:15:18,912
What's inside the package?

138
00:15:19,026 --> 00:15:21,279
Why are so many after it?

139
00:15:21,843 --> 00:15:23,230
You honestly don't know?

140
00:15:23,966 --> 00:15:26,148
Now that the Plum Flower Bandit reappeared

141
00:15:26,262 --> 00:15:27,815
lnside the package

142
00:15:27,931 --> 00:15:29,460
is the unique

143
00:15:29,567 --> 00:15:31,784
Gold Threaded Vest. lt's like an armour

144
00:15:34,612 --> 00:15:35,477
No wonder !

145
00:15:35,586 --> 00:15:37,246
Wine, sir

146
00:15:38,474 --> 00:15:39,410
Thanks

147
00:15:39,761 --> 00:15:42,121
Please let me go

148
00:15:42,231 --> 00:15:44,140
l'll give you everything

149
00:15:44,249 --> 00:15:45,601
l've an old grandmother

150
00:15:45,711 --> 00:15:47,857
Three children

151
00:15:50,407 --> 00:15:54,475
A lot of people are after this package

152
00:16:11,144 --> 00:16:13,088
So are you

153
00:16:13,196 --> 00:16:18,166
l kept my mouth shut before you had your tea

154
00:16:18,276 --> 00:16:21,371
Now that you've had a sip of poison tea

155
00:16:21,477 --> 00:16:24,014
... at the most l can wait here one more hour

156
00:16:24,121 --> 00:16:26,173
You'll die of poisoning

157
00:16:27,148 --> 00:16:29,164
l wasn't a part of it

158
00:16:30,697 --> 00:16:32,049
Who are you?

159
00:16:33,237 --> 00:16:34,766
Maybe you should know...

160
00:16:34,872 --> 00:16:36,816
who killed you !

161
00:16:38,873 --> 00:16:41,161
What a pretty girl

162
00:16:41,273 --> 00:16:45,235
l'd watch out should l see you again

163
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:48,151
Do you think you'll see me again?

164
00:16:48,266 --> 00:16:51,527
Of course, you know the tea is poisoned

165
00:16:51,642 --> 00:16:54,144
But you didn't know that when l was coughing

166
00:16:54,251 --> 00:16:56,468
... l spit out the tea

167
00:16:58,461 --> 00:16:59,397
Come on

168
00:17:37,914 --> 00:17:39,716
lmpressive !

169
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:51,692
Don't fight them. lf you use your energy

170
00:17:51,797 --> 00:17:55,925
... the poison inside you will circulate faster

171
00:17:59,172 --> 00:18:02,682
The girl forced me into poisoning the tea

172
00:18:03,451 --> 00:18:08,907
But l was responsible for poisoning the wine

173
00:18:09,471 --> 00:18:10,786
The wine too?

174
00:18:10,898 --> 00:18:12,700
Couldn't you taste it?

175
00:18:13,716 --> 00:18:15,174
You are ...

176
00:18:16,325 --> 00:18:19,623
One of the Seven lncredible Men

177
00:18:19,735 --> 00:18:24,041
The mean and shameless one ... Hua Feng

178
00:18:25,614 --> 00:18:27,001
l see

179
00:18:27,668 --> 00:18:29,257
Not anymore

180
00:18:29,372 --> 00:18:32,491
Now l'm the richest man in the martial arts world

181
00:18:32,608 --> 00:18:35,869
For l own the Gold Threaded Vest

182
00:18:36,852 --> 00:18:38,512
You ... you ...

183
00:18:38,801 --> 00:18:41,920
lt's called, Fisherman gains when snipe & clam fight

184
00:18:42,036 --> 00:18:43,459
You ... you ...

185
00:18:56,022 --> 00:18:58,275
Master

186
00:19:00,407 --> 00:19:01,865
Chuanjia

187
00:19:02,877 --> 00:19:03,908
Master

188
00:19:04,025 --> 00:19:04,570
Chuanjia

189
00:19:04,686 --> 00:19:05,657
Master

190
00:19:05,764 --> 00:19:06,664
Hurry, go after him

191
00:19:06,774 --> 00:19:07,710
Sure

192
00:19:17,628 --> 00:19:18,659
He is over there

193
00:19:27,787 --> 00:19:28,890
Dead !

194
00:19:29,562 --> 00:19:30,877
Maybe he's got the antidote

195
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:33,099
Be careful

196
00:19:33,215 --> 00:19:35,196
He could have other poisonous weapons

197
00:19:35,581 --> 00:19:37,312
Don't scratch yourself

198
00:19:37,425 --> 00:19:38,255
l know

199
00:19:42,957 --> 00:19:45,424
Nothing at all

200
00:19:46,610 --> 00:19:48,139
l knew it

201
00:19:48,245 --> 00:19:50,914
l'm never that lucky

202
00:19:51,864 --> 00:19:57,178
Excellent wine

203
00:20:04,527 --> 00:20:06,543
Where do you think you're going?

204
00:20:06,825 --> 00:20:09,292
Despite charging us, you didn't treat the patient

205
00:20:09,399 --> 00:20:12,388
What'd you mean by coming here and drinking wine ?

206
00:20:14,688 --> 00:20:16,632
Haven't you heard

207
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:21,331
... that l've a habit ?

208
00:20:21,437 --> 00:20:22,682
What habit?

209
00:20:22,794 --> 00:20:27,135
l don't treat patients when l drink

210
00:20:28,257 --> 00:20:30,582
Damn it, l'll kill you

211
00:20:32,292 --> 00:20:36,182
l wouldn't treat the patient, if you want to kill me

212
00:20:38,033 --> 00:20:40,286
Let's talk this over

213
00:20:40,398 --> 00:20:41,713
No one needs to get hurt

214
00:20:41,825 --> 00:20:43,734
Mind your own business

215
00:20:49,792 --> 00:20:52,294
Don't run

216
00:20:52,402 --> 00:20:54,904
Don't run

217
00:20:55,011 --> 00:20:56,398
Don't run

218
00:20:58,038 --> 00:21:01,027
Odd indeed that the one who is telling us not to run

219
00:21:01,134 --> 00:21:06,341
... is instead running away himself !

220
00:21:10,598 --> 00:21:14,239
Do you now know who l am?

221
00:21:14,877 --> 00:21:17,414
Sorry, may l know your name?

222
00:21:18,252 --> 00:21:19,355
ln that case...

223
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:22,731
You save me not because you wanted my cure

224
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,376
Why do we need your help to cure us?

225
00:21:28,028 --> 00:21:31,361
Your master's poisoned by my Cold Chicken powder

226
00:21:31,473 --> 00:21:33,002
l'm the only one who can cure him

227
00:21:33,108 --> 00:21:35,124
No one else can

228
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:42,288
Someone stole the powder from me a year ago

229
00:21:42,398 --> 00:21:45,102
And now you've been poisoned

230
00:21:45,216 --> 00:21:46,283
Come on,

231
00:21:46,399 --> 00:21:50,705
Nothing is better than drinking to death

232
00:21:51,026 --> 00:21:54,015
Let's have a drink first

233
00:21:54,122 --> 00:21:56,447
Mr. Mei, you said you'll cure my master

234
00:21:56,558 --> 00:21:58,182
Why are you drinking?

235
00:21:59,793 --> 00:22:04,478
Why should trivial matters such as life and death

236
00:22:04,595 --> 00:22:06,291
... get in the way of drinking?

237
00:22:06,404 --> 00:22:11,611
lf you don't give me some wine, l won't help

238
00:22:19,486 --> 00:22:20,517
Master

239
00:22:20,947 --> 00:22:22,643
Come on

240
00:22:26,444 --> 00:22:28,140
You know that our master...

241
00:22:28,253 --> 00:22:30,850
can only live for two more hours?

242
00:22:30,967 --> 00:22:33,434
Why aren't you doing anything?

243
00:22:37,683 --> 00:22:40,981
l wouldn't be Mei Er...

244
00:22:41,091 --> 00:22:43,202
if you know when l've cured you

245
00:22:43,805 --> 00:22:46,307
l've already cured him

246
00:22:54,243 --> 00:22:59,390
The wine is the antidote

247
00:23:01,236 --> 00:23:02,860
Thank you, doctor

248
00:23:03,254 --> 00:23:05,923
What are you doing?

249
00:23:06,281 --> 00:23:07,739
What are you doing here?

250
00:23:09,587 --> 00:23:11,211
l'm Tian Qi

251
00:23:11,326 --> 00:23:14,386
Please excuse my two friends

252
00:23:14,491 --> 00:23:16,400
l'm here to apologize for them

253
00:23:18,215 --> 00:23:20,088
Sounds good

254
00:23:20,198 --> 00:23:23,708
Someone's hurt by the Plum Blossom Bandit

255
00:23:23,816 --> 00:23:26,733
Could you treat him first?

256
00:23:27,052 --> 00:23:30,456
ls he badly injured ?

257
00:23:30,566 --> 00:23:33,555
A minor wound on his shoulders

258
00:23:33,662 --> 00:23:37,066
ls that it? Then l don't have to go personally

259
00:23:37,177 --> 00:23:40,059
Just take the medicine. Where is he ?

260
00:23:40,168 --> 00:23:41,413
Xingyun Manor

261
00:23:41,977 --> 00:23:42,522
Who's the injured person?

262
00:23:42,639 --> 00:23:44,620
Master Long Xiaoyun

263
00:24:00,174 --> 00:24:01,383
Xunhuan

264
00:24:01,496 --> 00:24:03,263
Yes, it's me

265
00:24:04,315 --> 00:24:07,754
You're really here

266
00:24:07,863 --> 00:24:12,655
l brought some medicine from Mei Er for you

267
00:24:14,961 --> 00:24:17,392
Plum Blossom Bandit has resurfaced !

268
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:21,604
Right, he's now in Baoding City

269
00:24:21,710 --> 00:24:23,856
He has injured many

270
00:24:23,972 --> 00:24:25,561
Where did it all take place ?

271
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,200
My back garden. The Plum...

272
00:24:27,312 --> 00:24:29,885
Blossom Forest in front of Cold Fragrance Chamber

273
00:24:30,269 --> 00:24:32,629
Why there?

274
00:24:34,235 --> 00:24:38,161
Because Lin Xianer lives there

275
00:24:38,271 --> 00:24:39,931
Who's Lin Xianer?

276
00:24:41,055 --> 00:24:45,538
The number one beauty of martial arts world

277
00:24:45,647 --> 00:24:47,699
Do you have any idea...

278
00:24:47,804 --> 00:24:51,350
how many have fallen head over heels for her?

279
00:24:53,927 --> 00:24:57,781
What's her connection to you, Brother Long?

280
00:24:57,893 --> 00:25:00,039
Why's she living in the Cold Fragrance Chamber?

281
00:25:00,364 --> 00:25:02,724
Let me fill you in the details

282
00:25:02,834 --> 00:25:05,194
l heard that Miss Lin's father...

283
00:25:05,304 --> 00:25:07,936
was killed by the Plum Blossom Bandit

284
00:25:08,053 --> 00:25:11,658
She has announced that...

285
00:25:11,775 --> 00:25:13,851
