309
00:27:37,241 --> 00:27:40,954
lf l don't drink, life seems like such a burden !

310
00:27:44,373 --> 00:27:48,928
Who told you to do so?

311
00:27:50,183 --> 00:27:51,463
Myself

312
00:27:52,341 --> 00:27:54,179
Why?

313
00:27:55,715 --> 00:27:59,297
Because l owe my life to someone

314
00:27:59,543 --> 00:28:03,148
To be benevolent to your savior you feigned idiocy

315
00:28:03,265 --> 00:28:08,686
You got drunk all the time, frequented the brothels

316
00:28:09,911 --> 00:28:14,074
Yes, l was hoping you'd give up on me

317
00:28:14,190 --> 00:28:15,684
... and marry Long Xiaoyun

318
00:28:16,208 --> 00:28:20,371
Do you think l'd be happy?

319
00:28:23,444 --> 00:28:26,599
After you've left

320
00:28:26,715 --> 00:28:29,419
l found out the truth

321
00:28:31,273 --> 00:28:33,775
l wanted to kill myself

322
00:28:34,787 --> 00:28:37,491
And then l thought...

323
00:28:37,605 --> 00:28:39,194
l'd better stay alive

324
00:28:40,492 --> 00:28:46,364
Because there's a chance we'll see each other again

325
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:52,347
Too bad, things have changed now

326
00:28:54,374 --> 00:29:03,485
The past is in the past

327
00:29:15,772 --> 00:29:17,266
Lady Lin

328
00:29:26,592 --> 00:29:27,766
Where's Master Li?

329
00:29:28,157 --> 00:29:29,615
He's right here

330
00:29:34,908 --> 00:29:37,825
Master Li, all the guests have arrived

331
00:29:37,934 --> 00:29:40,638
