332
00:29:41,205 --> 00:29:42,272
Please

333
00:29:43,953 --> 00:29:46,764
Let me introduce you

334
00:29:46,876 --> 00:29:49,164
My sworn brother Li Xunhuan

335
00:29:49,276 --> 00:29:50,734
Li Ning of Wudang Clan

336
00:29:50,842 --> 00:29:51,458
Pleased to meet you

337
00:29:51,572 --> 00:29:52,639
Golden Fist Deng Lie

338
00:29:52,756 --> 00:29:53,372
Delighted

339
00:29:53,486 --> 00:29:54,457
Wang Chen, Golden Palms of Hua Shan

340
00:29:54,565 --> 00:29:55,074
Pleased to meet you

341
00:29:55,190 --> 00:29:56,992
Master Tian Qi, the lron Sword

342
00:29:57,105 --> 00:29:58,350
Delighted

343
00:29:58,461 --> 00:30:01,865
This is the renowned Master Gongsun

344
00:30:01,975 --> 00:30:03,742
Pleased to meet you

345
00:30:05,872 --> 00:30:08,683
Master Li was a legendary character ten years ago

346
00:30:08,795 --> 00:30:12,270
