347
00:30:12,378 --> 00:30:13,931
Same here

348
00:30:20,345 --> 00:30:24,793
He's Longsheng, young master of Hidden Sword Manor

349
00:30:25,321 --> 00:30:30,006
He's proud and aloof, with incredible swordplay

350
00:30:30,121 --> 00:30:34,249
Nonetheless he is infatuated with Lin Xianer

351
00:30:34,366 --> 00:30:38,043
He's most eager to have Plum Blossom Bandit dead

352
00:30:38,403 --> 00:30:39,932
Master Zhao is here

353
00:30:44,457 --> 00:30:45,595
Master Zhao

354
00:30:45,709 --> 00:30:48,935
Sorry l am late

355
00:30:49,049 --> 00:30:51,718
No problem

356
00:30:51,832 --> 00:30:55,058
Master Zhao, why are you here with so much gold?

357
00:30:55,172 --> 00:30:56,487
There is a saying:

358
00:30:56,599 --> 00:30:59,445
lt's everyone's duty to rid the society of evils

359
00:31:00,078 --> 00:31:04,277
l hate the pests of the society

360
00:31:04,392 --> 00:31:06,929
That's why l'm here today

361
00:31:07,037 --> 00:31:09,183
l hope to eliminate a public enemy

362
00:31:09,297 --> 00:31:11,170
And l brought along 10,000 taels of gold as...

363
00:31:11,281 --> 00:31:13,534
a reward for the one who kills Plum Blossom Bandit

364
00:31:17,404 --> 00:31:19,456
Where's Miss Lin?

365
00:31:43,568 --> 00:31:46,308
Miss Lin ...

366
00:31:51,361 --> 00:31:53,021
Please sit down

367
00:31:56,615 --> 00:31:59,876
My father was murdered, l can't wait to get my revenge

368
00:31:59,990 --> 00:32:02,101
That's why l take this opportunity here

369
00:32:02,216 --> 00:32:04,956
... to say this in person

370
00:32:05,765 --> 00:32:07,841
Whoever kills the Plum Blossom Bandit

371
00:32:07,957 --> 00:32:10,317
regardless of age, status and wealth

372
00:32:10,428 --> 00:32:13,345
l, Lin Xianer, will keep my promise to marry him

373
00:32:16,794 --> 00:32:19,463
What Miss Lin is about to do...

374
00:32:19,577 --> 00:32:21,344
