377
00:32:33,008 --> 00:32:34,502
This is ...

378
00:32:34,607 --> 00:32:38,153
My sworn brother Li Xunhuan

379
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:42,915
No wonder he's so good with the daggers

380
00:32:43,792 --> 00:32:44,859
Have you two met?

381
00:32:44,976 --> 00:32:48,095
Yes, and l've offended him

382
00:32:48,211 --> 00:32:50,915
Can l have a word with Master Li alone?

383
00:32:51,029 --> 00:32:52,203
Certainly

384
00:32:59,727 --> 00:33:02,015
You should know why l'm here

385
00:33:02,127 --> 00:33:04,108
You need that Gold Threaded Vest

386
00:33:04,493 --> 00:33:05,951
because you'll go up against the Plum Blossom Bandit

387
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:06,925
That's right

388
00:33:07,382 --> 00:33:08,627
ls that it?

389
00:33:10,409 --> 00:33:12,425
lf you want to find out more...

390
00:33:12,531 --> 00:33:15,235
Meet me here at midnight

391
00:33:15,349 --> 00:33:16,807
And l'll let you know the details

392
00:34:07,015 --> 00:34:09,375
There have been two deaths here

393
00:34:09,485 --> 00:34:12,367
One is the younger brother of the Master lron Flute

394
00:34:12,477 --> 00:34:15,394
The other is the only son of Master Zhao Zhengyi

395
00:34:15,504 --> 00:34:18,659
They died at midnight

396
00:34:18,774 --> 00:34:20,718
Why at midnight?

397
00:34:20,827 --> 00:34:23,496
Because people say the Plum Blossom Bandit

398
00:34:23,610 --> 00:34:25,792
always shows up around midnight

399
00:34:29,803 --> 00:34:30,870
The Plum Blossom Bandit ?

400
00:34:50,818 --> 00:34:53,320
Longsheng... young master of Hidden Sword Mansion

401
00:34:53,427 --> 00:34:54,707
That's me

402
00:35:19,243 --> 00:35:20,346
Why do you want to kill me?

403
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:22,227
Someone wants me to kill you

404
00:36:11,953 --> 00:36:14,977
Hurry... inside

405
00:36:15,084 --> 00:36:16,578
Look

406
00:36:21,138 --> 00:36:22,205
Master You?

407
00:36:22,321 --> 00:36:23,257
Someone over there

408
00:36:29,001 --> 00:36:29,760
What's going on?

409
00:36:29,871 --> 00:36:31,116
Who told you to come here?

410
00:36:31,227 --> 00:36:31,878
Miss Lin Xianer

411
00:36:31,993 --> 00:36:33,380
Bullshit

412
00:36:33,489 --> 00:36:36,121
Miss Lin Xianer has left in the evening

413
00:36:36,238 --> 00:36:38,040
l saw her off personally

414
00:36:38,778 --> 00:36:40,093
That can't be,

415
00:36:40,204 --> 00:36:42,671
l was just talking to her earlier

416
00:36:42,779 --> 00:36:44,961
lf she hasn't told me to meet her here

417
00:36:45,075 --> 00:36:46,320
... what would l be doing here?

418
00:36:46,431 --> 00:36:47,640
To kill

419
00:36:48,067 --> 00:36:48,932
To kill?

420
00:36:49,041 --> 00:36:50,108
That's right

421
00:36:55,721 --> 00:36:59,789
At midnight the Plum Blossom Bandit will show up

422
00:36:59,896 --> 00:37:01,034
A concerned person

423
00:37:02,993 --> 00:37:04,131
At midnight,

424
00:37:04,245 --> 00:37:05,941
you killed Master You

425
00:37:06,054 --> 00:37:06,813
Get him

426
00:37:16,318 --> 00:37:18,785
You've got it all wrong

427
00:37:18,892 --> 00:37:20,481
We all were set up in a trap

428
00:37:20,597 --> 00:37:22,957
Let's sit down and talk this over

429
00:37:23,067 --> 00:37:24,075
We're not interested

430
00:37:27,834 --> 00:37:29,945
Looks like all of you...

431
00:37:30,061 --> 00:37:32,943
are hell bent to kill me now

432
00:37:35,384 --> 00:37:36,451
Don't come any closer

433
00:37:37,158 --> 00:37:40,740
That was a warning,

434
00:37:40,846 --> 00:37:44,285
next time it's gonna be for real

435
00:37:49,266 --> 00:37:52,421
Zhao Zhengyi, you said earlier that

436
00:37:52,536 --> 00:37:54,374
you want to get rid of the pests in society?

437
00:37:55,181 --> 00:37:56,841
Why don't you do something !

438
00:38:01,061 --> 00:38:04,216
Right, are you waiting for Master Tian Qi ?

439
00:38:04,330 --> 00:38:06,797
Or Master Gongsun ?

440
00:38:07,115 --> 00:38:08,502
Xunhuan, Xunhuan

441
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:14,242
That's so strange, you all wanted me dead

442
00:38:14,351 --> 00:38:16,011
Why don't you do something?

443
00:38:16,681 --> 00:38:18,068
l think you've got it wrong

444
00:38:18,178 --> 00:38:19,493
My sworn brother won't be the Plum Blossom Bandit

445
00:38:19,604 --> 00:38:20,956
Xunhuan, please hold your temper

446
00:38:21,066 --> 00:38:22,595
Brother Long

447
00:38:25,415 --> 00:38:27,740
Master Zhao, we must kill him today

448
00:38:28,651 --> 00:38:30,204
What are you doing?

449
00:38:30,668 --> 00:38:32,577
Stop it, everyone

450
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,294
Let him go first

451
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,953
No matter what crime he has done

452
00:38:37,070 --> 00:38:38,872
... l'll take full responsibility

453
00:38:39,123 --> 00:38:40,510
We just can't let the Plum Blossom Bandit walk away

454
00:38:40,619 --> 00:38:42,208
That's right

455
00:38:43,506 --> 00:38:46,138
Xunhuan, why don't you tell them ...

456
00:38:46,255 --> 00:38:47,429
that you're no Plum Blossom Bandit?

457
00:38:48,482 --> 00:38:51,506
lt took them a while to catch a suspect

458
00:38:51,613 --> 00:38:53,380
l don't want to ruin their excitement

459
00:38:59,824 --> 00:39:00,855
Chuanjia

460
00:39:08,139 --> 00:39:08,790
Let's go, young master

461
00:39:08,905 --> 00:39:10,636
Chuanjia

462
00:39:11,062 --> 00:39:12,070
Xunhuan

463
00:39:13,428 --> 00:39:16,132
Do you remember the day we first met?

464
00:39:16,246 --> 00:39:17,491
The Justice Eight accused you for

465
00:39:17,603 --> 00:39:19,785
... killing their head Meng Tianjie

466
00:39:19,899 --> 00:39:22,853
l told you to leave just like you're doing now

467
00:39:22,961 --> 00:39:24,490
You remember what you said then?

468
00:39:24,596 --> 00:39:25,841
l said l didn't kill anyone

469
00:39:25,953 --> 00:39:27,862
l won't leave...

470
00:39:27,971 --> 00:39:29,002
before this matter is cleared up

471
00:39:29,745 --> 00:39:31,761
Then why are you telling me to leave now?

472
00:39:32,981 --> 00:39:36,005
l think you won't believe l'm the Plum Blossom Bandit!

473
00:39:37,121 --> 00:39:39,030
But before they get to the bottom of all this...

474
00:39:39,138 --> 00:39:40,525
they shouldn't hurt you now

475
00:39:40,635 --> 00:39:43,790
There's no need for further investigation. We're right

476
00:39:43,906 --> 00:39:44,842
He is the Plum Blossom Bandit

477
00:39:44,949 --> 00:39:45,980
Shut up

478
00:39:47,767 --> 00:39:49,047
Ah Fei

479
00:39:56,361 --> 00:39:57,985
Who are you? What do you want?

480
00:39:58,310 --> 00:40:00,907
Who are you? What do you want?

481
00:40:02,519 --> 00:40:04,143
l want to teach you a lesson

482
00:40:14,139 --> 00:40:15,277
My friend

483
00:40:19,045 --> 00:40:24,157
Very impressive, at such a young age

484
00:40:24,264 --> 00:40:27,383
l'm Zhao Zhengyi, the impartial person

485
00:40:27,500 --> 00:40:29,717
And your name is ?

486
00:40:29,831 --> 00:40:31,942
l want to be your friend

487
00:40:32,648 --> 00:40:34,071
l don't have a name,

488
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:36,053
and l don't want you as my friend

489
00:40:42,112 --> 00:40:43,048
Your package

490
00:40:44,165 --> 00:40:45,718
So you killed Hua Feng

491
00:40:45,835 --> 00:40:48,789
That's right, he was carrying the package

492
00:40:48,897 --> 00:40:50,806
l knew he couldn't be a good person

493
00:40:50,915 --> 00:40:53,797
l went back to look for you, but you weren't there

494
00:40:53,906 --> 00:40:56,017
Then l found out you're here

495
00:40:57,769 --> 00:40:59,429
What's going on?

496
00:40:59,856 --> 00:41:02,216
They said l'm the Plum Blossom Bandit

497
00:41:02,953 --> 00:41:03,924
Bullshit

498
00:41:04,344 --> 00:41:05,553
Come on, let's go for a drink

499
00:41:05,666 --> 00:41:06,602
Wait

500
00:41:06,884 --> 00:41:10,489
lt's just the Plum Blossom Bandit we're after

501
00:41:10,606 --> 00:41:13,725
You shouldn't get involved

502
00:41:13,843 --> 00:41:15,539
Who said he's the Plum Blossom Bandit?

503
00:41:15,652 --> 00:41:17,905
l said so

504
00:41:30,995 --> 00:41:31,338
Shiyin

505
00:41:31,447 --> 00:41:32,347
What's going on?

506
00:41:32,457 --> 00:41:33,702
l have no idea

507
00:41:51,348 --> 00:41:55,167
Tell the others that you're the Plum Blossom Bandit

508
00:41:55,384 --> 00:41:56,249
Are you crazy?

509
00:41:56,359 --> 00:41:58,505
How would l be the Plum Blossom Bandit ?

510
00:42:02,968 --> 00:42:05,541
l'll ask you one more time

511
00:42:05,648 --> 00:42:09,289
This is your last chance. Are you ?

512
00:42:12,049 --> 00:42:15,038
Yes, l'm the Plum Blossom Bandit

513
00:42:18,034 --> 00:42:20,501
You heard him, everyone

514
00:42:20,608 --> 00:42:22,660
lf his word is to be trusted...

515
00:42:22,765 --> 00:42:24,389
He is the Plum Blossom Bandit

516
00:42:25,548 --> 00:42:28,085
Young man, that's not fair

517
00:42:28,193 --> 00:42:30,968
l mean this is how the martial world functions

518
00:42:31,081 --> 00:42:33,369
The one with the quickest sword is the boss

519
00:42:49,102 --> 00:42:50,454
So?

520
00:42:51,260 --> 00:42:52,813
Anyone else?

521
00:42:58,740 --> 00:42:59,356
Let's go

522
00:42:59,471 --> 00:43:00,265
Wait

523
00:43:01,385 --> 00:43:04,339
How do you know l'm not that Bandit ?

524
00:43:05,107 --> 00:43:08,405
l grew up in the wilderness, like an animal

525
00:43:08,517 --> 00:43:11,612
l've an instinct to distinguish good and evil

526
00:43:11,996 --> 00:43:13,490
lf l leave now...

527
00:43:13,597 --> 00:43:14,700
They will be more certain that

528
00:43:14,814 --> 00:43:17,067
... l'm the suspect

529
00:43:17,945 --> 00:43:19,605
Xunhuan is right

530
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:21,973
He can leave when we're sure of the facts

531
00:43:22,991 --> 00:43:24,793
Right

532
00:43:24,904 --> 00:43:27,192
Fine, l'll be in the deserted temple in the outskirts

533
00:43:27,304 --> 00:43:28,312
Come look for me should you need me

534
00:43:28,418 --> 00:43:29,069
Great

535
00:43:30,019 --> 00:43:31,027
Young brother

536
00:43:33,219 --> 00:43:36,588
l don't need the Gold Threaded Vest, you take this

537
00:43:44,387 --> 00:43:46,463
l got it, bye

538
00:44:13,578 --> 00:44:15,903
So you're here for the package

539
00:44:20,676 --> 00:44:21,612
The Plum Blossom Bandit?

540
00:44:29,582 --> 00:44:30,827
You got hit with my Plum Blossom Nails

541
00:44:30,939 --> 00:44:32,219
You shouldn't be able to move

542
00:44:46,491 --> 00:44:48,602
Li Xunhuan was right

543
00:44:48,718 --> 00:44:51,220
He knew someone would come after this vest

544
00:44:51,327 --> 00:44:52,227
Before l left

545
00:44:52,336 --> 00:44:55,005
He told me to wear it

546
00:45:20,691 --> 00:45:22,315
Very impressive

547
00:45:35,548 --> 00:45:36,615
What are you doing here?

548
00:45:36,730 --> 00:45:38,983
Here's your belongings. Leave now

549
00:45:39,096 --> 00:45:40,649
Why must l leave?

550
00:45:40,767 --> 00:45:44,480
Can't you tell they're doing this on purpose?

551
00:45:46,264 --> 00:45:48,375
l've suspected it,

552
00:45:48,490 --> 00:45:51,122
since the first day l came back to the country,

553
00:45:51,239 --> 00:45:53,741
there's a trap waiting for me

554
00:45:54,404 --> 00:45:57,665
The Gold Threaded Vest, Lin Xianer

555
00:45:57,780 --> 00:45:59,997
and now they call me the Plum Blossom Bandit

556
00:46:01,154 --> 00:46:02,885
Who is trying to hurt me?

557
00:46:02,998 --> 00:46:04,979
Since you know that someone's trying to hurt you

558
00:46:05,086 --> 00:46:07,030
You should better leave soon

559
00:46:08,426 --> 00:46:10,442
Have you seen the spider webs?

560
00:46:11,070 --> 00:46:12,350
Yes

561
00:46:13,645 --> 00:46:17,607
